Paper: hep-th/0210234

Date: 2002-10-24

Title: No horizons in pp-waves

Authors: Veronika E Hubeny and Mukund Rangamani

Comments: 19 pages, 1 figure, uses harvmac and epsf

Journal-ref: JHEP 0211 (2002) 021

We argue that pp-wave backgrounds can not admit event horizons. We alsocomment on pp-wave generalizations which would admit horizons and show thatthere exists a black string solution which asymptotes to a five dimensionalplane wave background.